      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total dream. This car is in stunning, showroom-ready condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and sparkling clean. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m happy to answer any questions or have you over for a test drive. Can't wait to see this beauty go to a great new home!",
